<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Registration - Make a Difference</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: url('/images/img5.jpg') no-repeat center center fixed;
            background-size: cover;
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .overlay {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Dark overlay for better text visibility */
        }

        .container {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            padding: 40px;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            border-radius: 10px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 500px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .quote {
            font-style: italic;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: #FFD700; /* Gold color for quote */
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        input[type="text"], input[type="email"], input[type="password"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #333;
        }

        button {
            background-color: #FFD700; /* Gold button */
            color: #333;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            width: 100%;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #FFBF00;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .already-account {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .already-account a {
            color: #FFD700;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .already-account a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        footer {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 5px;
            width: 100%;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #fff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <% if (errors && errors.length > 0) { %> <!-- Check if errors is defined -->
        <div style="color: red;">
            <% errors.forEach(function(error) { %>
                <p><%= error.msg %></p>
            <% }); %>
        </div>
    <% } %>
    <div class="overlay"></div>
    
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Join Us in Making a Difference</h1>
        <p>Every small act of kindness can create a ripple effect that changes lives. Your donation can help families in need, and together, we can make the world a better place.</p>
        <div class="quote">"The best way to find yourself is to lose yourself in the service of others." – Mahatma Gandhi</div>

        <form action="/auth/register" method="POST">
            <div class="form-group">
                <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Full Name" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email Address" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Password" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <input type="password" name="password2" placeholder=" Confirm Password" required>
            </div>

            <button type="submit">Register and Make a Difference</button>
        </form>
        <div class="already-account">
            <p>Already have an account? <a href="/auth/login">Log in here</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>© 2024 Make a Difference. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>